author: Alison Branley
title: 'A pretty messed up feeling': The horror of passing coronavirus to a friend
description: When musician Dan Williams returned from Japan he knew that put him at risk of coronavirus, but it was an Uber ride after he returned home that would prove the most likely culprit.
